[package]
name = "anime-game-core"
version = "1.32.2"
authors = [ "Nikita Podvirnyi <krypt0nn@vk.com>",]
license = "GPL-3.0"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/an-anime-team/anime-game-core"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
dns-lookup = "2.0"
serde_json = "1.0"
fs_extra = "1.3.0"
thiserror = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"
lazy_static = "1.5.0"

[features]
genshin = []
star-rail = []
zzz = []
honkai = []
pgr = []
wuwa = [ "dep:flate2", "dep:brotli-decompressor",]
sophon = [ "dep:md-5", "dep:zstd", "dep:reqwest", "dep:protobuf", "dep:protobuf-codegen",]
install = [ "external", "dep:sysinfo", "dep:zip", "dep:tar", "dep:xz", "dep:bzip2", "dep:flate2", "dep:md-5",]
external = [ "dep:kinda-virtual-fs",]
patches = []
patch-jadeite = []
patch-mfc140 = []
all = [ "install", "external", "patches", "sophon",]

[dependencies.minreq]
version = "2.13"
features = [ "json-using-serde", "https-rustls-probe", "proxy",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.cached]
version = "0.55"
features = [ "proc_macro",]

[dependencies.anyhow]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "backtrace",]

[dependencies.sysinfo]
version = "0.35"
optional = true
features = [ "linux-netdevs",]

[dependencies.zip]
version = "3.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.tar]
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.xz]
version = "0.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.bzip2]
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.flate2]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.md-5]
version = "0.10"
features = [ "asm",]
optional = true

[dependencies.kinda-virtual-fs]
version = "0.1.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.brotli-decompressor]
version = "4.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.zstd]
version = "0.13"
optional = true

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12"
features = [ "blocking", "h2", "http2", "json", "rustls-tls", "rustls-tls-webpki-roots", "socks",]
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.protobuf]
version = "3.7"
optional = true

[build-dependencies.protobuf-codegen]
version = "3.7.2"
optional = true

[package]
name = "anime-launcher-sdk"
version = "1.28.7"
authors = [ "Nikita Podvirnyi <krypt0nn@vk.com>",]
license = "GPL-3.0"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/an-anime-team/anime-launcher-sdk"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
tracing = "0.1"

[features]
genshin = [ "anime-game-core/genshin", "anime-game-core/sophon",]
star-rail = [ "anime-game-core/star-rail",]
zzz = [ "anime-game-core/zzz",]
honkai = [ "anime-game-core/honkai",]
pgr = [ "anime-game-core/pgr",]
wuwa = [ "anime-game-core/wuwa",]
star-rail-patch = [ "anime-game-core/patch-jadeite",]
honkai-patch = [ "anime-game-core/patch-jadeite",]
pgr-patch = [ "anime-game-core/patch-mfc140",]
wuwa-patch = [ "anime-game-core/patch-jadeite",]
states = []
config = [ "dep:serde", "dep:serde_json", "dep:enum-ordinalize",]
components = [ "dep:wincompatlib", "dep:lazy_static",]
game = [ "components", "config",]
sandbox = []
sessions = []
environment-emulation = []
fps-unlocker = [ "dep:md-5",]
all = [ "states", "config", "components", "game", "sandbox", "sessions", "environment-emulation", "fps-unlocker",]
default = [ "all",]

[dependencies.anime-game-core]
git = "https://github.com/an-anime-team/anime-game-core"
tag = "1.32.2"
features = [ "all",]

[dependencies.anyhow]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "backtrace",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.cached]
version = "0.55"
features = [ "proc_macro",]

[dependencies.enum-ordinalize]
version = "4.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.wincompatlib]
version = "0.7.7"
features = [ "all",]
optional = true

[dependencies.lazy_static]
version = "1.5.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.md-5]
version = "0.10"
features = [ "asm",]
optional = true

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/an-anime-team/anime-game-core"]
git = "https://github.com/an-anime-team/anime-game-core"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
tag = "1.32.2"

[source."https://github.com/an-anime-team/anime-launcher-sdk"]
git = "https://github.com/an-anime-team/anime-launcher-sdk"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
tag = "1.28.7"
